parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic shoulder belt can lead to inadequate restraint of the occupant, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The shoulder belt does not retract to its starting position
the shoulder belt does not close or lock up as designed
the shoulder belt detaches itself during impact
the shoulder belt fails to tighten
the shoulder belt snaps back tightly
pinning the driver to the seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can prevent the occupant from being properly restrained, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The driver's seat belt buckle fails to latch
the driver side seat belt buckle does not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the motorized belt can lead to inadequate restraint of the occupant, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The motorbelt failed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A short circuit in the ignition switch can cause a fire, potentially leading to vehicle damage, injury, or even fatalities.
symptoms: Fire under the hood
burning smell
smoke
or flames emanating from the ignition switch area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning automatic shoulder belt can cause the driver to feel insecure in their seat, potentially leading to accidents or injuries due to improper restraint.
symptoms: The automatic shoulder belt opens and closes when the door is shut
causing the driver to feel unstable or unsecured in their seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear axle can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities, especially when the vehicle is in motion.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
the rear axle seizes or locks up
the vehicle pulls to one side
the vehicle vibrates or shakes
the vehicle makes a loud grinding or screeching noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dealer Neglect and Failure to Address Safety Concerns
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of dealerships to address safety concerns and neglecting to properly diagnose and repair issues can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Dealership fails to diagnose or repair issues
despite repeated complaints
dealership dismisses or downplays safety concerns
dealership fails to provide adequate documentation or explanation of repairs.
